ent-RMCMedalRuby-desc = An exalted ruby medal, only able to be handed out by Generals due to special circumstances.
ent-RMCMedalRubyService-name = ruby service medal
ent-RMCMedalRubyService-desc = An Exalted ruby medal awarded for a marine's service within the UNMC; such medals are hand-given by UNMC Generals directly to a marine. It signifies the excessive amount of time a marine has spent in the line of duty.
