ent-RMCMedalAmethystService-name = amethyst service medal
ent-RMCMedalAmethystService-desc = A mythical amethyst medal awarded for a marine's service within the UNMC; such medals are hand-given by UNMC High Command directly to a marine. It signifies the unreasonable amount of time a marine has spent in the line of duty.
ent-RMCMedalEmerald-name = emerald medal
