ent-RMCMedalEmeraldService-name = emerald service medal
ent-RMCMedalEmeraldService-desc = A revered emerald awarded for a marine's service within the UNMC; such medals are hand-given by UNMC High Command directly to a marine. It signifies the exorbitant amount of time a marine has spent in the line of duty.
